    <!-- ===== TERMS OF SERVICE ===== -->
    <div id="terms" class="legal-doc">
      <h2 class="legal-doc-title">Terms of Service</h2>
      <p class="legal-date">Effective: July 2026</p>
      <div class="legal-body">
        <p>These Terms of Service govern your access to and use of the Mount Veritas website ("Site") and your purchase of products from Mount Veritas ("we," "us," "our"), operated from Calgary, Alberta, Canada. By accessing the Site or placing an order, you accept these Terms in full. If you do not agree, do not use the Site.</p>

        <h3>1. Eligibility</h3>
        <p>You must be at least 18 years of age, or the age of majority in your province or territory, to place an order. By placing an order, you confirm that you meet this requirement.</p>

        <h3>2. Products and Availability</h3>
        <p>All products are subject to availability. Product images are for illustrative purposes; actual colors may vary slightly due to display calibration and lighting. We reserve the right to limit quantities, discontinue products, or refuse orders at our sole discretion.</p>

        <h3>3. Pricing and Currency</h3>
        <p>All prices are displayed in Canadian Dollars (CAD) unless stated otherwise and are subject to change without notice. Applicable taxes are calculated and displayed at checkout. Prices do not include shipping charges, which are shown separately before you confirm your order.</p>

        <h3>4. Orders and Acceptance</h3>
        <p>Your submission of an order constitutes an offer to purchase. We reserve the right to accept or decline any order. A confirmed order does not constitute a binding contract until we send an order confirmation email. If a product is found to be incorrectly priced or described after order submission, we will contact you before proceeding or will cancel and refund the order in full.</p>

        <h3>5. Payment</h3>
        <p>We accept the payment methods displayed at checkout. By placing an order, you authorize us to charge your chosen payment method for the total amount including taxes and shipping. If payment is declined, we will cancel the order. You are responsible for providing accurate billing information.</p>

        <h3>6. Shipping</h3>
        <p>We currently ship within Canada and to the United States. Shipping is a flat 20 CAD on orders under 200 CAD, and free on orders of 200 CAD or more. Estimated delivery timeframes are provided at checkout and are not guaranteed. Risk of loss and title pass to you upon delivery of the goods to the carrier. We are not responsible for delays caused by the carrier, customs, or events outside our control. See our Shipping section for full details.</p>

        <h3>7. Returns and Refunds</h3>
        <p>You may cancel an order within 48 hours of purchase if it has not yet shipped. Unworn, unwashed items in their original condition with tags attached may be returned within 168 hours, which is 7 days, of the confirmed delivery date. Items marked final sale are not eligible. To start a return, contact us through our Contact page before shipping any item back. Refunds are processed to the original payment method within 5 to 10 business days of receiving and inspecting the returned item. Original shipping charges are non-refundable unless the return is due to our error or a defective product. See our Returns and Refunds section for the full process.</p>

        <h3>8. Discount Codes</h3>
        <p>Promotional codes are one-time use per customer unless otherwise stated. Codes cannot be combined with other promotions, applied to previous orders, or exchanged for cash value. We reserve the right to expire, modify, or revoke any code at any time.</p>

        <h3>9. Intellectual Property</h3>
        <p>All content on this Site, including but not limited to the Mount Veritas name, logo, wordmark, mountain mark, product designs, photography, copy, and all other materials, is the sole and exclusive property of Mount Veritas and is protected under applicable Canadian intellectual property law. Reproduction, distribution, or commercial use of any content without our prior written consent is strictly prohibited.</p>

        <h3>10. Limitation of Liability</h3>
        <p>To the fullest extent permitted by Alberta law, Mount Veritas will not be liable for any indirect, incidental, special, consequential, or punitive damages arising from your use of our Site or products. Our total liability for any claim arising under these Terms shall not exceed the purchase price of the specific product giving rise to the claim.</p>

        <h3>11. Governing Law and Jurisdiction</h3>
        <p>These Terms are governed by and construed in accordance with the laws of the Province of Alberta and the applicable federal laws of Canada. Any disputes shall be resolved exclusively in the courts of Calgary, Alberta.</p>

        <h3>12. Changes to These Terms</h3>
        <p>We may revise these Terms at any time by posting the updated version on this page with a new effective date. Your continued use of the Site following any change constitutes acceptance of the revised Terms.</p>

        <h3>13. Contact</h3>
        <p>Questions about these Terms: Mount Veritas, Calgary, Alberta, Canada. Use our <a href="/pages/contact-us">Contact page</a> to reach us.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- ===== RETURNS AND REFUNDS ===== -->
    <div id="returns" class="legal-doc">
      <h2 class="legal-doc-title">Returns and Refunds</h2>
      <p class="legal-date">Effective: July 2026</p>
      <div class="legal-body">
        <p>This section covers how to cancel an order and how to return a piece. It applies to everything sold by Mount Veritas.</p>
        <h3>Cancellations</h3>
        <p>You can cancel your order within 48 hours of placing it, as long as it has not shipped yet. Once an order has shipped it can no longer be cancelled, but you can return it under the terms below.</p>
        <h3>Returns</h3>
        <p>You have 168 hours, which is 7 days, from the confirmed delivery date to request a return. To be accepted, the piece must be unworn, unwashed, and in its original condition with any tags still attached. Items marked final sale are not eligible.</p>
        <p>To start a return, reach us through our <a href="/pages/contact-us">Contact page</a> with your order number within that window. We will confirm the return and send you the steps.</p>
        <h3>Refunds</h3>
        <p>Once your return is received and inspected, we issue your refund to the original payment method within 5 to 10 business days. Original shipping charges are not refunded. Any customs duties or taxes are not refunded.</p>
        <p>Return shipping for a change of mind is your responsibility. We recommend a tracked method, since we cannot refund a return that does not reach us.</p>
        <h3>Damaged or Wrong Items</h3>
        <p>If your order arrives damaged, defective, or incorrect, contact us within 48 hours of delivery through our <a href="/pages/contact-us">Contact page</a> with your order number and a clear photo. We will replace it or refund it in full, and we cover the return shipping in that case.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- ===== SHIPPING ===== -->
    <div id="shipping" class="legal-doc">
      <h2 class="legal-doc-title">Shipping</h2>
      <p class="legal-date">Effective: July 2026</p>
      <div class="legal-body">
        <h3>Order Processing</h3>
        <p>Orders arrive within 5 to 7 business days. Orders placed on weekends or holidays begin processing the next business day. You receive a confirmation with tracking once your order ships.</p>
        <h3>Rates</h3>
        <p>Shipping is a flat 20 CAD on orders under 200 CAD. Orders of 200 CAD or more ship free. Your rate is shown at checkout before you pay.</p>
        <h3>Where We Ship</h3>
        <p>We currently ship within Canada and to the United States.</p>
        <h3>Delivery</h3>
        <p>Delivery times are estimates and are not guaranteed. Actual times can vary with the carrier, the destination, and customs. Please allow 1 to 3 business days for tracking to begin updating after you receive it.</p>
        <h3>Customs and Duties</h3>
        <p>For orders shipped outside Canada, any customs fees, import duties, or taxes charged by the destination country are the responsibility of the customer. We have no control over these charges.</p>
        <h3>Package Protection</h3>
        <p>At checkout you can add package protection for 4.99. It covers loss, theft, or damage in transit so we can replace or refund your order quickly.</p>
        <h3>Lost or Damaged Packages</h3>
        <p>If your order arrives damaged, contact us within 48 hours of delivery through our <a href="/pages/contact-us">Contact page</a> with your order number and a photo. If a package is lost in transit, contact us and we will work with the carrier to resolve it.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- ===== PRIVACY POLICY ===== -->
    <div id="privacy" class="legal-doc">
      <h2 class="legal-doc-title">Privacy Policy</h2>
      <p class="legal-date">Effective: July 2026</p>
      <div class="legal-body">
        <p>Mount Veritas ("we," "us") is committed to protecting your personal information. This Privacy Policy describes how we collect, use, disclose, and protect information in accordance with the Personal Information Protection and Electronic Documents Act (PIPEDA) and the Alberta Personal Information Protection Act (PIPA).</p>

        <h3>1. Information We Collect</h3>
        <p>We collect information you provide directly when you place an order, create an account, subscribe to our newsletter, or contact us. This includes: name, email address, phone number, shipping and billing addresses, and the content of any message you send. We also automatically collect technical information such as your IP address, browser type, pages visited, time spent on pages, and device information through cookies and analytics tools.</p>

        <h3>2. How We Use Your Information</h3>
        <p>We use your personal information to: process and fulfill your orders; send order confirmations, shipping notifications, and related transactional emails; respond to your inquiries; send marketing and promotional communications if you have expressly consented; improve our Site and products; detect and prevent fraudulent transactions; and comply with our legal obligations. We do not sell, rent, or trade your personal information to third parties for their own marketing purposes.</p>

        <h3>3. Service Providers</h3>
        <p>Our Site is hosted on Shopify Inc. (Shopify), which processes certain data on our behalf as a data processor, subject to their Privacy Policy and Data Processing Agreement. Payment processing is handled by Shopify Payments and approved payment partners who are PCI-DSS compliant. We may use additional service providers for email delivery, analytics, and customer support, all of whom are bound by confidentiality and data processing obligations consistent with this Policy.</p>

        <h3>4. Marketing Communications (CASL)</h3>
        <p>We send marketing emails only to individuals who have expressly consented, in compliance with Canada's Anti-Spam Legislation (CASL). Consent may be given through checkout opt-in or our contact form. Each marketing email includes a one-click unsubscribe option. You may withdraw consent at any time by clicking "Unsubscribe" in any email or by contacting us directly. Withdrawal of consent does not affect the lawfulness of communications sent before withdrawal.</p>

        <h3>5. Cookies and Tracking</h3>
        <p>We use cookies to maintain your session, remember your cart, and analyze Site traffic. Strictly necessary cookies are required for the Site to function and cannot be disabled. Analytics and preference cookies are used to improve your experience; you may disable these through your browser settings, which may affect certain Site features.</p>

        <h3>6. Data Retention</h3>
        <p>We retain personal information for as long as necessary to fulfill the purposes described in this Policy or as required by law. Order and transaction records are retained for a minimum of seven years to satisfy our tax and accounting obligations. Marketing consent records are retained for as long as you remain subscribed plus a reasonable period thereafter.</p>

        <h3>7. Your Rights</h3>
        <p>Under PIPEDA and PIPA, you have the right to: access the personal information we hold about you; request corrections to inaccurate information; withdraw consent to certain processing; and request deletion of information we are not legally required to retain. To exercise any of these rights, contact us using the information below. We will respond within 30 days of receiving a complete request. We may need to verify your identity before processing your request.</p>

        <h3>8. Security</h3>
        <p>We implement commercially reasonable security measures, including encryption of data in transit via TLS, to protect your personal information. However, no method of electronic transmission or storage is completely secure, and we cannot guarantee absolute security. You are responsible for maintaining the confidentiality of any account credentials.</p>

        <h3>9. Children's Privacy</h3>
        <p>Our Site is not directed at individuals under the age of 18. We do not knowingly collect personal information from minors. If you believe we have inadvertently collected information from a minor, please contact us immediately.</p>

        <h3>10. Changes to This Policy</h3>
        <p>We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Material changes will be communicated by posting the revised Policy on this page with an updated effective date. Your continued use of the Site after any change constitutes your acceptance of the revised Policy.</p>

        <h3>11. Contact</h3>
        <p>Privacy inquiries: Mount Veritas, Calgary, Alberta, Canada. Use our <a href="/pages/contact-us">Contact page</a>. We will acknowledge your inquiry within 5 business days.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- ===== ACCESSIBILITY ===== -->
    <div id="accessibility" class="legal-doc">
      <h2 class="legal-doc-title">Accessibility Statement</h2>
      <p class="legal-date">Effective: July 2026</p>
      <div class="legal-body">
        <p>Mount Veritas is committed to ensuring that our website is accessible to everyone, including people with disabilities. We are actively working to conform to the Web Content Accessibility Guidelines (WCAG) 2.1, Level AA, published by the World Wide Web Consortium (W3C).</p>

        <h3>Our Commitment</h3>
        <p>We believe every person deserves equal access to our products and content. Accessibility is an ongoing effort, not a one-time exercise. We continually review and improve our Site as standards evolve and user feedback is received.</p>

        <h3>Current Measures</h3>
        <p>We have implemented the following accessibility measures: semantic HTML5 markup; descriptive alt text on all meaningful images; sufficient color contrast ratios for text and interactive elements; keyboard-navigable menus, forms, and interactive components; ARIA labels on custom UI controls; visible focus indicators; and responsive design that supports browser text resizing and zoom up to 200% without loss of content or functionality.</p>

        <h3>Known Limitations</h3>
        <p>While we strive for full WCAG 2.1 AA conformance, some sections of our Site may not yet fully meet this standard. We are working to identify and remediate any gaps. Third-party tools and embedded services, including our checkout, are managed by Shopify Inc.; we encourage you to review their Accessibility Statement for information on their own conformance efforts.</p>

        <h3>Request Accommodation</h3>
        <p>If you encounter an accessibility barrier on our Site, or if you require our content in an alternative format, please contact us through our <a href="/pages/contact-us">Contact page</a>. Please describe the accessibility issue and the format you need, and we will do our best to respond within 5 business days with the requested content or an alternative solution.</p>

        <h3>Feedback</h3>
        <p>Your feedback is important to us. We welcome suggestions on how we can improve the accessibility of this Site. Contact us at any time through our <a href="/pages/contact-us">Contact page</a>.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>

